  "text": "Shear wave propagation direction. Amplitude-weighted shear wave propagation directions were estimated by directionally filtering the curl of the displacement field. [CITATION_1] The curl (Γ = ∇ × u) is advantageous to use because it contains no contributions from rigid-body motion or longitudinal waves.",
